dc_description_s: This point data layer represents addresses for Outagamie County, Wisconsin in 2014.[This is a 'point' feature class representing the location where the driveway meets the road right of way. It contains the House Number and Street Name (Address). The parcel number is also included for each address 'point'.]
uw_supplemental_s: This metadata was updated to reflect that the data is no longer restricted and has been opened for public use.Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For complete metadata documentation, please visit: http://data-ocgis.opendata.arcgis.com/
